WEBVTT

00:00.587 --> 00:03.480
<i>Take out the translator,
that's all we asked you to do.</i>

00:03.500 --> 00:04.510
This is what
the interpreter had.

00:06.380 --> 00:09.350
<i>There's a former MI6
officer here looking for her.</i>

00:09.370 --> 00:10.490
Who did you talk to, Adam?

00:10.510 --> 00:13.360
I'm not abandoning her
for a second time.

00:13.380 --> 00:14.400
You think about the people

00:14.420 --> 00:16.400
you serve, Senator.

00:16.420 --> 00:17.480
<i>They want me to back off</i>

00:17.500 --> 00:19.320
this whole Mali thing.

00:19.340 --> 00:22.360
Everywhere your troops go
in this war

00:22.380 --> 00:24.290
<i>on terror, it just seems</i>

00:24.310 --> 00:25.320
to get worse.

00:25.340 --> 00:26.290
We're never gonna get anywhere

00:26.310 --> 00:27.480
while she has
the president's ear.

00:27.500 --> 00:31.370
I need you to put a police van
inside this checkpoint.

00:31.390 --> 00:33.350
Who is the president's
closest ally?

00:33.370 --> 00:34.400
Aminata Sissoko.

00:34.420 --> 00:36.370
We have to bring the threat

00:36.390 --> 00:37.500
to his front door, Joseph.

00:42.350 --> 00:43.490
<i>Get your guys
to find Harry Clarke.</i>

00:43.510 --> 00:45.330
<i>You follow him to Aicha.</i>

00:45.350 --> 00:47.360
<i>If I know him, he'll find her.</i>

00:51.480 --> 00:53.350
Where are we going?

00:54.490 --> 00:57.420
We have to get out of here,
out of Bamako.

00:57.440 --> 01:00.320
Harry, she's in a bad way.

